{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@_NSRange","text":"NSRange"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"range"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"withCoordinates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"coords"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"count:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSUInteger","text":"NSUInteger"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"count"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"range","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The range of vertices to replace. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"location"},{"type":"text","text":" field indicates"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the first vertex you are replacing, with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":" being the first vertex, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"being the second vertex, and so on. The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"length"},{"type":"text","text":" field indicates the number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of vertices to replace."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"coords","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of coordinates defining part of the shape. The data in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this array is copied to the shape’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"count","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The number of coordinates from the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coords"},{"type":"text","text":" array to insert in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"place of the coordinates in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"range"},{"type":"text","text":". The sum of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"range"},{"type":"text","text":"’s length and this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"count must not exceed the number of items currently in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the shape is currently visible on the map as an annotation, it is redrawn"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"immediately. If the shape is part of an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" object, you must"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"explicitly set the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/shape"},{"type":"text","text":" property in order for any style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layers that use the source to be redrawn."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" is greater than the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"length"},{"type":"text","text":" field of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"range"},{"type":"text","text":", some vertices will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"effectively be inserted into the shape. On the other hand, if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" is less"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"length"},{"type":"text","text":" field of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"range"},{"type":"text","text":", some vertices will effectively be removed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"range"},{"type":"text","text":" extends beyond the shape’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinates"},{"type":"text","text":" property, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSRangeException"},{"type":"text","text":" is raised. If you want to append new vertices to the shape,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-appendCoordinates:count:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint\/replacecoordinatesinrange:withcoordinates:count:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:"}],"title":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPoint(im)replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"replaceCoordinatesInRange:withCoordinates:count:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Replaces the vertices at the given range in the shape with the specified number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of vertices from a given C array."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoi